---
// FAQ Section Component
---

<section id="faq" class="w-full max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 mb-24 md:mb-32 relative z-10">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-medium text-white font-manrope mb-4">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-400">Everything you need to know about our crypto tax reconciliation process.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-4">
        <!-- FAQ Item 1 -->
        <div class="bg-zinc-900/40 border border-white/5 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden transition-all hover:border-white/10">
            <details class="group">
                <summary class="flex items-center justify-between p-6 cursor-pointer list-none">
                    <h4 class="text-white font-semibold text-lg">What if my transaction history is a total mess?</h4>
                    <span class="text-orange-500 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"/></svg>
                    </span>
                </summary>
                <div class="px-6 pb-6 text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed">
                    We specialize in unraveling years of trading chaos. Our data specialists and AI tools are designed to identify gaps, fix cost basis issues, and clean up messy data that other platforms or accountants can't handle.
                </div>
            </details>
        </div>

        <!-- FAQ Item 2 -->
        <div class="bg-zinc-900/40 border border-white/5 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden transition-all hover:border-white/10">
            <details class="group">
                <summary class="flex items-center justify-between p-6 cursor-pointer list-none">
                    <h4 class="text-white font-semibold text-lg">Can you handle multiple wallets and exchanges?</h4>
                    <span class="text-orange-500 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"/></svg>
                    </span>
                </summary>
                <div class="px-6 pb-6 text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed">
                    Yes, we support all major wallets and exchanges. Whether you have 2 or 200, we consolidate all your data into a single source of truth for your tax filing.
                </div>
            </details>
        </div>

        <!-- FAQ Item 3 -->
        <div class="bg-zinc-900/40 border border-white/5 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden transition-all hover:border-white/10">
            <details class="group">
                <summary class="flex items-center justify-between p-6 cursor-pointer list-none">
                    <h4 class="text-white font-semibold text-lg">What if I have complex DeFi or staking transactions?</h4>
                    <span class="text-orange-500 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"/></svg>
                    </span>
                </summary>
                <div class="px-6 pb-6 text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed">
                    That's our specialty. We decode complex blockchain activity like liquidity mining, bridging, staking rewards, and yield farming that generic tax software often misclassifies.
                </div>
            </details>
        </div>

        <!-- FAQ Item 4 -->
        <div class="bg-zinc-900/40 border border-white/5 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden transition-all hover:border-white/10">
            <details class="group">
                <summary class="flex items-center justify-between p-6 cursor-pointer list-none">
                    <h4 class="text-white font-semibold text-lg">What about legal gray areas?</h4>
                    <span class="text-orange-500 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"/></svg>
                    </span>
                </summary>
                <div class="px-6 pb-6 text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed">
                    We provide legal opinion letters through our partner, Olson & Partners Law, for complex situations where the tax law may be unclear. This provides you with a defensible position in case of an IRS inquiry.
                </div>
            </details>
        </div>

        <!-- FAQ Item 5 -->
        <div class="bg-zinc-900/40 border border-white/5 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden transition-all hover:border-white/10">
            <details class="group">
                <summary class="flex items-center justify-between p-6 cursor-pointer list-none">
                    <h4 class="text-white font-semibold text-lg">How does pricing work?</h4>
                    <span class="text-orange-500 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"/></svg>
                    </span>
                </summary>
                <div class="px-6 pb-6 text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed">
                    Every situation is unique. We'll discuss your specific data volume and complexity on our call and provide transparent, upfront pricing. There are no hidden fees.
                </div>
            </details>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    details > summary {
        list-style: none;
    }
    details > summary::-webkit-details-marker {
        display: none;
    }
</style>

